{"id": 1089, "genre": 1001, "title": "【好奇心x宋】你有哪些珍爱生命的细节？", "description": "换句话说，你对安全这件事有哪些执着到强迫的习惯？（题图来自：dreamstime）", "record_count": 5538, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160705193252L4AstKjTn35w0Y9H.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 3, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-07-06T03:03:11Z", "options": [{"id": 95291, "content": "买车前要看看碰撞性试验中假人死了没", "image": null, "praise_count": 76, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 95292, "content": "在超市里仔细查看食物的保质期和配料表", "image": null, "praise_count": 288, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 95419, "content": "在超市货架前，看完了零食的配料表，默默地把它们放回去……", "image": null, "praise_count": 164, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 169983}, {"id": 95293, "content": "遵循低GI饮食谱，每种食物精确到克", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 95295, "content": "拒绝滑板滑冰自行车攀岩，任何带有危险系数的运动方式", "image": null, "praise_count": 69, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 95346, "content": "化妆品成分控，一定要搞清楚里面有什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 95642, "content": "戴套", "image": null, "praise_count": 75, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 114717}, {"id": 95647, "content": "关弹幕，保智商~~~~~", "image": null, "praise_count": 75, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 504368}, {"id": 95648, "content": "遠離LOL", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 525930}, {"id": 95649, "content": "不吃过期食品", "image": null, "praise_count": 38, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 179207}, {"id": 95652, "content": "?不敢去美国；好多枪", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 425163}, {"id": 95654, "content": "少吃垃圾食品", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668979}, {"id": 95656, "content": "少吃点药", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668981}, {"id": 95657, "content": "少吃辣条", "image": null, "praise_count": 36, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668967}, {"id": 95744, "content": "进电梯前看看电梯有没有到", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 669290}, {"id": 95745, "content": "过没有红绿灯的马路，一定要左右三米范围内没有车才敢过", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 669283}, {"id": 104193, "content": "睡前手机关wifi", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 700756}, {"id": 95746, "content": "吃完油腻食物用要和茶去去油???", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 591404}, {"id": 95747, "content": "开车时避让电瓶车大大", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 611598}, {"id": 95748, "content": "雷雨天气导致的触电", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 669262}, {"id": 95750, "content": "睡覺前要檢查關沒關門", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 669375}, {"id": 95495, "content": "选择像宋这样的五星安全suv", "image": null, "praise_count": 83, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 95751, "content": "不管后面有没有车，变道都会打转向灯", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 490284}, {"id": 95752, "content": "不管是什麼東西都要查看所含成分是那些", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 669011}, {"id": 95753, "content": "买饮料钱看营养成分表 碳水超过4%就不买", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 411650}, {"id": 95754, "content": "活蹦乱跳惯了，突然在弹跳落地的1s内崴脚导致几周石膏不能出门，才意识到身体的脆弱，生命的可贵", "image": "img/option/option/20160706170748DQuja4ENq2gWhUl5.jpg", "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668518}, {"id": 95755, "content": "定期体检", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 598133}, {"id": 95756, "content": "丢掉炸猪扒的油", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 634834}, {"id": 95757, "content": "把手机放在脚那头?", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 536471}, {"id": 95758, "content": "睡前